 you’ll be notified. No need to monitor it yourself.\n\nHere’s what you get in the app:\n• Live monitoring of all electricity contracts\n• Alerts when it’s beneficial to switch providers\n• See how much you’ve saved\n• View electricity prices including grid fees\n• Electricity prices directly from Nord Pool\n• Your consumption data from Elhub\n• Slipper Community – suggest and vote on new features\n\nAlways on your side:\n• No ads – not even in the free version\n• No partnerships with electricity providers\n• We never sell your data\n\nWe focus on one thing: helping you make better electricity decisions.\nOver 100,000 people already use Slipper.\n\nTrack your consumption and electricity prices for free.\nFull access for NOK 299/year.","sellerUrl":"https://slipper.no/","userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":163,"languageCodesISO2A":["NB"],"averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":4.10429,"fileSizeBytes":"80629760","formattedPrice":"Free","trackContentRating":"4+","userRatingCount":163}